bestPractices:
 interaction of government agencies with business and development of a competitive environment.
The "Showcase of Services" platform provides solutions to the following tasks:

creation of a unified catalog of information system services of government agencies and the private sector with the provision of a technical description of the service and contact details of the owner of the service and the developer of the information system;
automation of the processes of obtaining access to services published on the portal of the Showcase of services through the gateway of "electronic government";
automation of the process of creating new information services of information systems through connectors (service constructor).
